  npcVisitFlavors:
  - recounts a route you would never find on your own.
  - names three towns past the ridge and says what each is worth visiting.
  - traces something in the dirt that might be a map, then scuffs it out.
  npcExchangeFlavors:
  - tucks a fistful of berries into your kit. Road food. Don't make a ceremony of
    it.
  - hands you a tally stick, carved with distances you don't quite recognize.
